ী থাক","audioUrl":"wbw/003_064_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56625,"position":30,"arabic":"بِأَنَّا","translation":"আমরা যে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_064_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56626,"position":31,"arabic":"مُسْلِمُونَ","translation":"(আল্লাহর অনুগত বান্দা) মুসলমান''","audioUrl":"wbw/003_064_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56627,"position":32,"arabic":"٦٤","translation":"(৬৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":65,"arabic":"يَٰٓأَهْلَ ٱلْكِتَٰبِ لِمَ تُحَآجُّونَ فِىٓ إِبْرَٰهِيمَ وَمَآ أُنزِلَتِ ٱلتَّوْرَىٰةُ وَٱلْإِنجِيلُ إِلَّا مِنۢ بَعْدِهِۦٓ ۚ أَفَلَا تَعْقِلُونَ","translation":"O FOLLOWERS of earlier revelation! Why do you argue about Abraham, seeing that the Torah and the Gospel were not revealed till [long] after him? Will you not, then, use your reason?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/358.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":57139,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَهْلَ","translation":"হে আহলে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57140,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْكِتَـٰبِ","translation":"কিতাব","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57141,"position":3,"arabic":"لِمَ","translation":"কেন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57142,"position":4,"arabic":"تُحَآجُّونَ","translation":"তোমরা বিতর্ক করছ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57143,"position":5,"arabic":"فِىٓ","translation":"প্রশ্নে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57144,"position":6,"arabic":"إِبْرَٰهِيمَ","translation":"ইবরাহীমের","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57145,"position":7,"arabic":"وَمَآ","translation":"অথছ না","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57146,"position":8,"arabic":"أُنزِلَتِ","translation":"নাযিল হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57147,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلتَّوْرَىٰةُ","translation":"তাওরাত","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57148,"position":10,"arabic":"وَٱلْإِنجِيلُ","translation":"ও ইনজীল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57149,"position":11,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57150,"position":12,"arabic":"مِنۢ","translation":"(থেকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57151,"position":13,"arabic":"بَعْدِهِۦٓ ۚ","translation":"তার পরে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57153,"position":14,"arabic":"أَفَلَا","translation":"না তবুও কি","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57154,"position":15,"arabic":"تَعْقِلُونَ","translation":"তোমরা বুঝবে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_065_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57155,"position":16,"arabic":"٦٥","translation":"(৬৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":66,"arabic":"هَٰٓأَنتُمْ هَٰٓؤُلَآءِ حَٰجَجْتُمْ فِيمَا لَكُم بِهِۦ عِلْمٌۭ فَلِمَ تُحَآجُّونَ فِيمَا لَيْسَ لَكُم بِهِۦ عِلْمٌۭ ۚ وَٱللَّهُ يَعْلَمُ وَأَنتُمْ لَا تَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"Lo! You are the ones who would argue about that which is known to you; but why do you argue about something which is unknown to you? Yet God knows [it], whereas you do not know:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/359.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":57470,"position":1,"arabic":"هَـٰٓأَنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরাই তো","audioUrl":"wbw/003_066_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57471,"position":2,"arabic":"هَـٰٓؤُلَآءِ","translation":"ঐ সব লোক (যারা)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_066_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57472,"position":3,"arabic":"حَـٰجَجْتُمْ","translation":"বিতর্ক করেছ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_066_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57473,"position":4,"arabic":"فِيمَا","translation":"সে বিষয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_066_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57474,"position":5,"arabic":"لَكُم","translation":"তোমাদের (আছে)","audioUr